"Otevřete zprávu od Czech BMX a potvrďte registraci. Pokud e-mail nevidíte "
"během několika minut, zkontrolujte i složku spam nebo hromadné."
msgstr ""
"Open the message from Czech BMX and confirm the registration. If you don't "
"see the email within a few minutes, check your spam or bulk folder as well."

msgid ""
"Po aktivaci se budete moct přihlásit stejným e-mailem a heslem, které jste "
"právě zadali."
msgstr ""
"After activation, you will be able to log in with the same email and "
"password you just entered."

